!Mouse Events
OnDesktop Mouse1 :HideMenus
OnDesktop Mouse2 :WorkspaceMenu
OnDesktop Mouse3 :RootMenu
OnDesktop Mouse4 :PrevWorkspace
OnDesktop Mouse5 :NextWorkspace

!Workspaces
Mod4 1 :SendToWorkspace 1
Mod4 2 :SendToWorkspace 2
Mod4 3 :SendToWorkspace 3
Mod4 4 :SendToWorkspace 4

Mod1 1 :Workspace 1
Mod1 2 :Workspace 2
Mod1 3 :Workspace 3
Mod1 4 :Workspace 4

!Navigation
Mod1 Tab :NextWindow
Mod1 Shift Tab :PrevWindow
Control Next :NextTab
Control Prior :PrevTab

!Windows-like Keys
Mod1 F4 :Close
Mod4 D :ToggleCmd {ShowDesktop} {DeIconify all originquiet}
Control Mod1 L :Exec xscreensaver-command -lock

!Fluxbox
Mod4 Space :Exec fbrun
Scroll_Lock :Exec fbrun
Control Mod1 Delete :Exec xkill
Mod4 Shift R :Restart 
Control Mod1 BackSpace :Exec exit

!Window Managment
Mod4 Mod1 Right :MoveRight 20
Mod4 Mod1 Left :MoveLeft 20
Mod4 Mod1 Up :MoveUp 20
Mod4 Mod1 Down :MoveDown 20

Shift Mod1 Right :Resize +10 -0
Shift Mod1 Left :Resize -10 -0
Shift Mod1 Up :Resize -0 -10
Shift Mod1 Down :Resize -0 +10

!Executables
Mod1 F3 :Exec xterm 
Mod4 F3 :Exec gnome-terminal
Mod4 N :Exec nautilus --no-desktop --browser

Mod4 P :Exec pidgin
F9  :Exec pidgin
F10 :Exec calagenda
F11 :Exec thunar
F12 :Exec firefox
